            <h2 class="console-title text-center" style="color: #D1D5DB; font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 8px;">STRATEGIC DEFENSE MODULES</h2>
            <p class="text-center" style="color: #9CA3AF; margin-bottom: 32px;">Implementing controls across the core defense triad: Governance, Infrastructure, and Personnel.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-8" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);">
                <!-- Governance Card (Policy) -->
                <div class="strategy-card" style="border-left-color: #FBBF24;">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="card-icon icon-policy"><i class="fas fa-gavel fa-lg"></i></div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #E5E7EB; font-weight: bold; margin-left: 16px;">GOVERNANCE PROTOCOLS</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #FBBF24;">Information Tiers:</strong> Formally structure and categorize data sensitivity levels (Public, Restricted, Sensitive).</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #FBBF24;">Access Minimization:</strong> Enforce the principle of **Least Privilege**. Grant users the absolute minimum required permissions.</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #FBBF24;">Usage Agreement:</strong> Clearly articulate the permitted and prohibited methods for handling and transmitting organizational data.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Infrastructure Card (Technology) -->
                <div class="strategy-card" style="border-left-color: #6366F1;">
                     <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
