                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #E5E7EB; font-weight: bold; margin-left: 16px;">INFRASTRUCTURE TOOLS</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #6366F1;">Leak Prevention Systems:</strong> Utilize software to monitor, detect, and halt unauthorized transmission of sensitive data.</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #6366F1;">Configuration Audits:</strong> Employ Cloud Security Posture Management (CSPM) to continually check for system misconfigurations.</li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #6366F1;">Identity Hardening:</strong> Mandate **Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)** for all system access points to secure identities.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <!-- Personnel Card (People) -->
                <div class="strategy-card" style="border-left-color: #34D399;">
