                         <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #34D399;">Social Engineering Tests:</strong> Conduct internal phishing simulations to gauge and strengthen employee vigilance.</li>
                         <li style="margin-bottom: 12px;"><strong style="color: #34D399;">Incident Reporting:</strong> Implement transparent and straightforward mechanisms for employees to safely report suspected security events.</li>
